cs/Slides), MarkusPfundstein/mcp-gsuite (GSuite interaction). LibreOffice: WaterPistolAI/libreoffice-mcp (17 stars, Python — Writer/Calc/Impress/Draw/Base, charts, formulas), patrup/mcp-libre (embedded MCP in LibreOffice, native integration), harshithb3304/libre-office-mcp (Python, document bridge). Generic Spreadsheet: PSU3D0/spreadsheet-mcp (39 stars, Rust — token-efficient, formula recalculation engine, batch operations, diff detection). Microsoft Official: microsoft/mcp (2,800 stars, C# — Azure MCP &#43; Fabric MCP, catalog of official Microsoft MCP servers). Full Office Automation: OfficeMCP/OfficeMCP (63 stars, Python — Word/Excel/Outlook/PowerPoint/Access/OneNote/Visio/Project via COM). Gaps: no real-time collaborative editing, no OneDrive MCP, no Notion-to-Office bridge, no spreadsheet visualization/charting-only server, no Apple Numbers, no WPS Office, no conflict resolution for concurrent edits. 35&#43; servers across 6 subcategories. Rating: 4/5.</description>
