les), cablate/mcp-google-map (13 tools including directions/distance-matrix), tomtom-international/tomtom-mcp (official — routing, traffic data), baidu-maps/mcp (official — driving/walking/cycling/transit routing). Gaps: no BMW/Mercedes/Hyundai/Ford brand-specific MCP servers, no ADAS/autonomous driving simulation integration, no insurance/claims, no tire/parts inventory, no repair shop management, no parking, no car wash, no ride-sharing/taxi dispatch. 20&#43; servers across 6 subcategories. Rating: 3/5.</description>
