      <description>Legal and contract management MCP servers are bringing AI agents into law offices, contract workflows, and regulatory research. We reviewed 50&#43; servers across 6 subcategories. E-Signature &amp; Document Signing: SendForSign MCP (official, document templates and signature workflows), SignNow MCP (official, template management, embedded signing, document downloads), caffeinebounce/docuseal-mcp-server (DocuSeal integration for templates and submission tracking), bmbouter/mcp-dropbox-sign (Dropbox Sign API for signature requests and templates), esignaturescom/mcp-server (contract and template management), signbee/signbee-mcp (markdown/PDF signing with certified delivery), esign-cn-open-source e签宝 MCP (Chinese e-signature with PDF conversion). Legal Research &amp; Case Law: JamesANZ/us-legal-mcp (comprehensive U.S. legislation via government APIs), khizar-anjum CourtListener MCP (3,352 U.S. courts), JustlyAI/DocketBird MCP (court document search), pylegifrance MCP (French Legifrance API), metaneutrons German Legal MCP (federal/state/EU legislation), Ansvar-Systems/Danish-law-mcp (Danish Retsinformation), seo-jinseok Korean Law MCP (statutes/precedents/administrative rules), saidsurucu Yargı MCP (Turkish Supreme/Constitutional Court decisions), groundcobra009 Hourei MCP (Japanese e-Gov Law API), russellbrenner AusLaw MCP (Australian legislation and case law), mickey-mikey OLEXI MCP (AustLII search), self-tech-labs Entscheidsuche MCP (Swiss court decisions), self-tech-labs Online Kommentar MCP (Swiss legal commentaries), numikel Law Scrapper MCP (Polish Sejm API), frontalinilucas saij-mcp (Argentine SAIJ database), jmtanguy Droit Français MCP (French Légifrance and JudiLibre), Mortalus eu-regulations (37 EU regulations including GDPR/AI Act/DORA). Legal Reasoning &amp; Document Generation: yoda-digital/mcp-cerebra-legal-server (enterprise-grade legal reasoning), automatikstudio LegalForge MCP (jurisdiction-specific document generation), agentic-ops/legal-mcp (comprehensive legal workflow server), Lexpedite Blawx MCP (rule-based legal reasoning with ontologies). IP &amp; Trademark: john-walkoe USPTO MCP (Final Petition Decisions API), saidsurucu Marka Patent MCP (Turkish trademark database), handaas Trademark Big Data MCP (fuzzy search and portfolio analysis). Compliance &amp; Regulatory: TCoder920x open-legal-compliance-mcp (multi-jurisdiction legal compliance via government APIs), eludden35 HIPAA Guardian MCP (healthcare compliance guidance), ethanolivertroy FedRAMP Docs MCP (FedRAMP requirements and security controls), Mortalus eu-regulations MCP (37 EU regulations), ag2-mcp-servers Policy Analyzer (Google Policy Analyzer API), negraodenio code-guard-ai (multi-LLM compliance orchestrator), Elnino0009 RegGuard MCP (financial marketing compliance). Legal Operations: DatSciX-CEO LumenX MCP (legal spend intelligence), lawmem-ai (persistent semantic memory for legal AI), visotrust/viso-mcp-server (legal document management), chapirousIA PJE MCP (Brazilian Electronic Judicial Process), VibeCoding4-JC PDP MCP (Indonesian data protection law RAG). Rating: 3.5/5.</description>
