      <description>IoT and embedded MCP servers are bridging AI agents and the physical world via the Model Context Protocol. We reviewed 45&#43; servers across 9 subcategories. Smart home leads with Home Assistant&#39;s official MCP integration plus community servers like tevonsb/homeassistant-mcp (500 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 20&#43; tools for entity control/monitoring). Robotics: robotmcp/ros-mcp-server (873 stars, Python, Apache-2.0 — bidirectional ROS/ROS2 control, most starred IoT MCP server). IoT platforms: thingsboard/thingsboard-mcp (official, Python, Apache-2.0, 120&#43; tools — largest tool count in the category). MQTT: ezhuk/mqtt-mcp (Python — building automation, industrial control, smart home), Benniu/emqx-mcp-server (EMQX Cloud&#43;self-hosted), CorefluxCommunity/Coreflux-MQTT-MCP-Server (enterprise TLS). ESP32/Arduino: horw/esp-mcp (135 stars, Python, MIT — ESP-IDF build/flash/fix), navado/ESP32MCPServer (C&#43;&#43; MCP on-device), mcp2everything/mcp2serial (33 stars, hardware control via serial). Raspberry Pi: grammy-jiang/RaspberryPiOS-MCP (GPIO/I2C/SPI/camera). Industrial IoT: AWS IoT SiteWise MCP (official, 20&#43; tools), kukapay/opcua-mcp (OPC UA nodes), cadugrillo/s7-mcp-bridge (Siemens S7 PLCs). 3D printing: DMontgomery40/mcp-3D-printer-server (61 stars, multi-platform STL operations), OctoEverywhere/mcp (official, OctoPrint/Klipper/Bambu Lab). Smart home devices: tuya/tuya-mcp-sdk (official), rmrfslashbin/hue-mcp (Philips Hue multi-bridge), thomasvincent/home-mcp (Apple HomeKit). Also: drone control, Bluetooth scanning, Zigbee2MQTT, Node-RED integration, CO2 sensors. Rating: 4.0/5.</description>
