      <description>Education and LMS MCP servers are connecting AI agents to learning management systems, study tools, and educational content via the Model Context Protocol. We reviewed 30&#43; servers across 7 subcategories. Canvas LMS dominates with 6&#43; implementations: vishalsachdev/canvas-mcp (Python, 90&#43; tools and 8 agent skills — FERPA-compliant data anonymization, rubric-based bulk grading, code execution), DMontgomery40/mcp-canvas-lms (60 stars, TypeScript, MIT — 54 tools for courses/assignments/enrollments/grades), aryankeluskar/canvas-mcp (TypeScript — dual Canvas&#43;Gradescope integration with Gemini-powered search), 54yyyu/school-mcp (TypeScript — Canvas&#43;Gradescope&#43;macOS Calendar), r-huijts/canvas-mcp (TypeScript — Claude Desktop Extension with privacy-first design). Moodle: peancor/moodle-mcp-server (27 stars, Python, MIT — 8&#43; tools for student management, assignments, quizzes, grading with write access). Google Classroom: faizan45640/google-classroom-mcp-server (Python, MIT — 3 tools with Google OAuth). Brightspace: pranav-vijayananth/brightspace-mcp-server (Python, Apache-2.0 — Playwright-based scraping with Duo 2FA). Educational Content: EduBase/MCP (Node.js — full e-learning platform with advanced quiz parametrization, SCORM support, cheating detection), Cicatriiz/openedu-mcp (TypeScript, MIT — 20&#43; tools aggregating OpenLibrary/Wikipedia/arXiv/Dictionary APIs with grade-level filtering), odewahn/orm-discovery-mcp (official O&#39;Reilly Learning Platform search). Spaced Repetition: ankimcp/anki-mcp-server (TypeScript — 27 tools for full Anki integration with deck sync, card review, media files, ngrok tunneling). Coding Education: jinzcdev/leetcode-mcp-server (57&#43; stars, TypeScript, MIT — dual leetcode.com/leetcode.cn support with tag/difficulty search), SPerekrestova/interactive-leetcode-mcp (TypeScript — guided DSA learning with progressive 4-level hints). Math &amp; Tutoring: clouatre-labs/math-mcp-learning-server (Python, MIT — 12&#43; tools for calculation, statistics, plotting, math tutoring), moarshy/mcp-tutor (Python — transforms GitHub docs into interactive lessons). Academic Research: mcp-for-research (TypeScript — unified PubMed/Google Scholar/arXiv/JSTOR interface), Semantic Scholar and Google Scholar MCP servers. Notable gaps: no Blackboard, Khan Academy, Coursera, edX, Duolingo, or PowerSchool MCP servers. Instructure (Canvas vendor) announced IgniteAgent with MCP support — first major LMS vendor to adopt MCP officially. Rating: 3.5/5.</description>
